=begin pod

=TITLE role Metamodel::RolePunning

=SUBTITLE Metaobject that supports I<punning> of roles.

    role Perl6::Metamodel::RoleContainer {}

Implements the ability to create objects from Roles without the intermediate
need to use a class.

=for code
role A {
    method b {
      return "punned"
    }
};
my $a = A.new;
say $a.b; # OUTPUT: «punned␤»

=end pod
